import {  Card, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'


const SingleBook = (props) => 
(
<Container>
<Card style={{width:'18rem'}}>
  <Card.Img variant="top" src={props.strive.img} />
  <Card.Body>
    <Card.Title>{props.strive.title}</Card.Title>
  </Card.Body>
</Card>
</Container>
)

export default SingleBook
